episodes.title: Get to Know Me - Unconventional Upbringing & The world outside is a Different Cult?
episodes.description:
Hey everyone, welcome to my channel!  I'm excited to embark on this journey of getting to know you all.

In this video, I'm cracking open the door to my past and sharing some stories about my upbringing. Let's just say, it wasn't your average childhood experience. There were definitely some unique rules and a perspective on the world that wasn't exactly mainstream.

Leaving that world behind was a big adjustment, but guess what? Stepping outside, I realized there might be a whole different kind of "cult" out here in the everyday world!

Intrigued? In this video, I'll share some stories about my unconventional background and how it shaped my view of the world.  Let me know in the comments what you think, and what other things you'd like to see in future videos!

Don't forget to subscribe for more videos and like this one if you found it interesting!

#UnveilingMe #UnconventionalUpbringing #CultLife #Perspective
#GetToKnowMe
